name: look at the stars, look how they shine for you
wishText: Allahumma thawal'umurana washah ajsadana wanawir qulubana watsabit imanana wa ahsan u'malana wawasi'arzaqana wa ilalkhoiri qarabna wa'anisy syahri ab'idna waqdhi khawaijana fid daini wad dunnya wal akhirat innaka 'ala kuli syai'in qadir.
